    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a perfectly synchronized double-VANOS system. The chassis has been meticulously preserved, including a proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a full refresh of the suspension geometry with high-durometer bushings. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The vehicle exhibits flawless compression numbers, zero parasitic fluid loss, and a factory-fresh finish. A turn-key specimen for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
