    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true 'time capsule' specimen that defines the term 'mint condition.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, retaining its original showroom luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark on the factory paint. The interior remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery shows zero bolster wear, and the cabin still retains its original factory scent. Every electronic component, from the precision infotainment system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service portfolio with all maintenance performed exclusively by authorized technicians. It sits on a fresh set of premium tires and has recently undergone a full multi-point inspection and fluid service. For the discerning collector or enthusiast seeking a flawless driving experience without compromise, this car offers unparalleled quality and documented provenance.",
